Text:
Thanks for this seed!

FYI:
From Blackomre's Night Official Web Page:
Blackmore's Kingdom - BEWARE, THIS CD IS A FAKE! THIS IS NOT BLACKMORE'S NIGHT!
Also note:
'Blackmore's Kingdom' is not affiliated with Ritchie Blackmore or Blackmore's Night.
Blackmore's Kingdom is a fake?  Good job I downloaded it, then... shame because it has some good music on it, too.
GOD.I LOVE WHEN PEOPLE DON'T KNOW HOW TO TAG MP3S OR EVEN GET THE FILENAMES CORRECTLY!!!!!
An extra copy of "Sake of the Song" seems to have been spliced onto the end of "Again Someday", starting at 1:59. Otherwise, excellent seed, and thank you.
Blackmore's Kingdom is actually the reason I downloaded this... dunno who it is exactly, but it's great.
